I use the Venus Comfortglide Razor, it has built-in soap bars with avocado oil that make every glide buttery smooth and super gentle.
Quick, easy, no pain, and no mess. Just wet, glide, moisturise and I’m done in 10 minutes!

💙 Proud to be part of the Venus Glide Girl Broadcast; for those of us who believe, “Always Venus.”
